The online help system performs the following functions:

  ~FG.help~RS              - displays a list of main topics
  ~FG.help credits~RS      - displays this talker's credits
  ~FG.help credits nuts~RS - displays the NUTS credits
  ~FG.help commands~RS     - displays the command list (also ~FG.commands~RS)
  ~FG.help <topic>~RS      - diplays information about <topic>, if found
